help.title: Silvanus Help
help.info:
Silvanus is the ultimate Grow A Tree companion bot! Quickly compare your server's tree to others on the leaderboard with automatic calculation of tree height differences, active growth detection, watering time calculations, and more!

Important Note: Silvanus is only as up-to-date as your server's newest Tree and Tallest Trees messages. Make sure to refresh them before refreshing Silvanus' Compare message.
help.setup:
If your </tree:972648557796524032> and </top trees:1051840665362894950> messages are in the same channel, simply run </compare:1065346941166297128> in that channel and you're good to go!

Otherwise, run </setup compare:1065407649363005561> to set the proper channels for the bot to look in for the </tree:972648557796524032> and </top trees:1051840665362894950> messages.

Use </commands:1077058896469966888> to view a description of all my commands.
help.permissions: At a minimum, Silvanus requires permissions to `Send Messages` and `Send Messages in Threads` if applicable. If Analyzer is given permission to `Manage Messages`, the bot will delete the `.settree` and `.setranks` messages to reduce spam.
help.allCommands:
</compare:1077058896469966889> - Compare your tree to others on the leaderboard
</relay set:0> - Setup a Notification Relay for the first time
</relay update:0> - Update an already configured Notification Relay
</relay disable:0> - Disable the Notification Relay
</rolemenu:1077058896469966892> - Send a self-assignable role menu for relay pings
</watertime:1077058896469966895> - Calculates the time between waters for a tree of a given height
</timetoheight:1077058896469966894> - Calculates how long it would take a tree to grow to a given height
</setup compare:1077058896469966893> - Set the channels to use with </compare:1077058896469966889>
</setup view:1077058896469966893> - View your server's configuration
</setup reset:1077058896469966893> - Delete your server's configuration
</help:1077058896469966890> - Displays the bot's help page
